headline: Dollar General Claims Yang Ming Owes $14.8M Over Failure to Fulfill Contract
summary: The discount retailer claims the carrier diverted reserved cargo space to higher-paying customers, leading the company to seek costlier space elsewhere.

headline: Amazon Is Going to Offer Fast Delivery in Rural Areas. Should Dollar General Investors Be Worried?
summary: Amazon is investing billions to expand its delivery network.  Dollar General's already thin margins could get squeezed even further.  Targeting rural areas has enabled Dollar General (NYSE: DG) to generate solid growth for years.
